.TH LOA-LIST-GENRE 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
list genre \- Show books by exact genre name
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> list genre <name>
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Matches the genre case-insensitively.
.TP
If <name> is omitted, the app prompts for the genre.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> list genre Fantasy
.TP
alexandria> list genre Sci-Fi
